{% extends 'emails/base.html.twig' %}

{% block content %}
    <h3 style="margin-top:0;">Welcome to Fantasy Academy, {{ userName|default('Manager') }}!</h3>

    <p>
        You’ve just joined a passionate community of aspiring Fantasy Premier League pros —
        people who live for the thrill of the game and the art of building a winning squad.
    </p>

    <callout class="secondary">
        <p style="margin:0;">
            At <strong>Fantasy Academy</strong>, we believe that FPL success isn’t luck —
            it’s a skill you can learn, train, and master.
            Here, you’ll find weekly challenges, expert insights, and tools designed to sharpen
            your decision-making and give you the edge over your rivals.
        </p>
    </callout>

    <spacer size="12"></spacer>

    <h5>What’s next?</h5>
    <ul>
        <li>Complete your first <strong>Challenge</strong> to start your training.</li>
        <li>Join the <strong>Community League</strong> to test your skills.</li>
        <li>Track your progress as you climb the Academy ranks.</li>
    </ul>

    <spacer size="8"></spacer>

    <button href="{{ dashboardUrl|default('https://fantasy-academy.com') }}" class="large expanded radius">
        Start My Journey
    </button>

    <spacer size="12"></spacer>

    <p>
        This is your moment — the start of your rise from a casual manager to an FPL tactician
        with the skills to outthink the competition.
        Let’s make it happen.
    </p>

    <p style="margin-bottom:0;">
        See you in the Academy,<br>
        <strong>The Fantasy Academy Team</strong>
    </p>
{% endblock %}
